---
source: src/core/curate.rs
assertion: review session propose uses persisted evidence spans
schema:
  session: ee.review.session.v1
contracts:
  - empty session returns no candidates
  - single-topic session with fewer than 2 spans returns no candidates
  - multi-topic session groups spans by topic key
  - each candidate requires at least 2 evidence spans
  - candidate IDs are deterministic given same inputs
  - propose mode persists candidates to curation queue
  - dry-run mode prevents persistence
evidence:
  - sessions.id
  - sessions.cass_session_id
  - evidence_spans.session_id
  - evidence_spans.excerpt
  - curation_candidates.workspace_id
  - curation_candidates.source_id
